title: Episode 374: Measure These...(Feat. Spice)
itunes:title: Episode 374: Measure These...(Feat. Spice)
description:
The "Queen of Dancehall," Spice, joins the ladies of Lip Service this week to promote her latest album 'Emancipated.' The ladies discuss a range topics including sex demons and their relationship with masturbating, how many times per week should one have sex, whether or not a**eating is overrated, and much more. Spice even brings out the tape measure and two model men to show the ladies how to properly know if he's packing without having to see him naked. Enjoy!
